messages.message:
Trying to run a flow and getting this message:
*Failed to run flow*

All records had a runtime exception. Last error observed was: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0).

trying to figure out what that means
Have you ticked force_image_ocr on Process file step config?

if you updated the ocr settings for your flow, sometimes it fills in the “page range” and “encryption config” with your email and password. This is what I have seen throw the error anyways

You can delete those fields.
Thanks Will - that was the issue - page range and Encryption had values
great catch @wadams Happened to me many times too :disappointed:
